---
title: Golden Coconut Tilapia with Green Onion Rice and Stir-Fried Veggies
description: Get ready for crunchy satisfaction from tender tilapia coated in shredded coconut and panko breadcrumbs! No need to get messy with deep-frying, you'll oven-bake these tilapia while cooking up some veggies and rice for an easy weeknight feast.
